Description: 1 fragment of papyrus with demotic text on front and back in columns. The fragment is semi-circular and is mounted with a photograph of the painted cartonnnage from which is was (presumably) extacted. Traces of red paint survive on the front.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380817) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380817)
